---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '../data/site.json';
---

<BaseLayout title={`About — ${site.title}`} description="Learn more about me, my skills, and the tools I work with.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="animate-fade-in-up mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">
        <span data-i18n-id>Tentang Saya</span><span data-i18n-en>About Me</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
        <span data-i18n-id>Kenali lebih dekat siapa saya, keahlian yang saya miliki, dan apa yang saya kerjakan.</span>
        <span data-i18n-en>Learn more about me, my skills, and the tools I work with.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed scroll-reveal">
      <p>
        <span data-i18n-id>Hai! Saya <strong class="text-text dark:text-slate-200">{site.name}</strong>, developer yang bersemangat membangun aplikasi web yang bersih dan skalabel. Saya senang bekerja dengan teknologi modern seperti Laravel, React, dan berbagai tool lainnya di ekosistem web.</span>
        <span data-i18n-en>Hi! I'm <strong class="text-text dark:text-slate-200">{site.name}</strong>, a developer passionate about building clean, scalable web applications. I enjoy working with modern stacks like Laravel, React, and various other tools in the web ecosystem.</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <span data-i18n-id>Saya percaya menulis kode yang tidak hanya fungsional, tapi juga mudah dipelihara dan terdokumentasi dengan baik. Di waktu luang, saya suka berbagi yang telah dipelajari melalui tulisan blog dan kontribusi open-source.</span>
        <span data-i18n-en>I believe in writing code that is not only functional but also maintainable and well-documented. When I'm not coding, I like sharing what I've learned through blog posts and open-source contributions.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Skills -->
    <div class="mt-16 scroll-reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-white">
        <span data-i18n-id>Keahlian & Alat</span><span data-i18n-en>Skills & Tools</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {[
          'Laravel', 'React', 'TypeScript', 'PHP', 'JavaScript',
          'Tailwind CSS', 'PostgreSQL', 'MySQL', 'Docker', 'Git',
          'Node.js', 'REST APIs', 'Linux', 'Astro',
        ].map((skill) => (
          <span class="rounded-full border border-border dark:border-slate-600 bg-surface dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            {skill}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About section extras -->
    <div class="mt-16 scroll-reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-white">
        <span data-i18n-id>Apa yang Saya Kerjakan</span><span data-i18n-en>What I Do</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            <span data-i18n-id>Pengembangan Full Stack</span><span data-i18n-en>Full Stack Development</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
            <span data-i18n-id>Pengembangan aplikasi web dari ujung ke ujung, dari desain database hingga tampilan frontend yang pixel-perfect.</span>
            <span data-i18n-en>End-to-end web application development from database design to pixel-perfect frontends.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            <span data-i18n-id>Menulis Teknis</span><span data-i18n-en>Technical Writing</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
            <span data-i18n-id>Berbagi pengetahuan melalui tulisan blog, dokumentasi, dan tutorial.</span>
            <span data-i18n-en>Sharing knowledge through blog posts, documentation, and tutorials.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            <span data-i18n-id>Desain API</span><span data-i18n-en>API Design</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
            <span data-i18n-id>Merancang dan membangun RESTful API yang bersih, terdokumentasi, dan mudah digunakan.</span>
            <span data-i18n-en>Designing and building RESTful APIs that are clean, well-documented, and easy to consume.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-slate-200">
            <span data-i18n-id>DevOps & Deployment</span><span data-i18n-en>DevOps & Deployment</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
            <span data-i18n-id>Menyiapkan CI/CD pipeline, kontainerisasi dengan Docker, dan manajemen server.</span>
            <span data-i18n-en>Setting up CI/CD pipelines, containerization with Docker, and server management.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
